Example qPCR data

Experimental variables include:

qpcr_names

Format

qPCR sample names in 96 well format.

Details

  • cell line (wt, mut)

  • gene (IFN, ACTIN)

  • time (0, 12, 24, 48)

  • reverse transcriptase (+, -)

  • replicate (1, 2, 3)

Varaibles are encoded in samples names: cell_time_gene_rt_rep.

Examples

qpcr_names
#> # A tibble: 8 x 13
#>     row             `1`              `2`              `3`              `4`
#>   <chr>           <chr>            <chr>            <chr>            <chr>
#> 1     A mut_0_ACTIN_+_1    mut_0_IFN_+_2 mut_12_ACTIN_+_3 mut_24_ACTIN_+_1
#> 2     B mut_0_ACTIN_-_1    mut_0_IFN_-_2 mut_12_ACTIN_-_3 mut_24_ACTIN_-_1
#> 3     C mut_0_ACTIN_+_2    mut_0_IFN_+_3   mut_12_IFN_+_1 mut_24_ACTIN_+_2
#> 4     D mut_0_ACTIN_-_2    mut_0_IFN_-_3   mut_12_IFN_-_1 mut_24_ACTIN_-_2
#> 5     E mut_0_ACTIN_+_3 mut_12_ACTIN_+_1   mut_12_IFN_+_2 mut_24_ACTIN_+_3
#> 6     F mut_0_ACTIN_-_3 mut_12_ACTIN_-_1   mut_12_IFN_-_2 mut_24_ACTIN_-_3
